          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">σχέτλιος</span></b>  (<span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἔχω</span>), <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">σχετλίη</span>, <i><span class="en">Il. 3.414</span></i>:
          properly, <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">holding out, enduring</span>, then in moral sense,
            <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">hard, hardened, perverse, cruel;</span>
