          but without serious reproach, <i><span class="en">Il.
            10.164</span></i>; of things in Od., <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἔργα, ὕπνος,
            ι 295</span>, <i><span class="en">Od.
          10.69</span></i>.</div> <div class="alpheios-lex-footnotes en"> </div>
